{"title":"Curve Cycling’s New Carbon Walmer Bar is Wide and Light","link":"https://theradavist.com/curves-new-carbon-walmer-bar-is-wide-and-light/","date":1707143617000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2255\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?fit=1200,2255&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?w=3840&amp;quality=75 3840w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?resize=1200,705&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?resize=2000,1174&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?resize=768,451&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?resize=1536,902&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer50.13Carbon.jpg?resize=2048,1203&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Announced today, <a href=\"https://www.curvecycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Curve Cycling</a>‘s popular wide and flared Walmer bar just <a href=\"https://www.curvecycling.com/products/carbon-walmer-bar?variant=42809612075184\" target=\"_blank\">got a redux in carbon</a> for a pricepoint of $301. Check out more information here…<span></span></p>\n<p>Curve’s ever-popular wide drop bar is now available in carbon. The Carbon Walmer is now available in three size options: 43, 46, 50 cm.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/IMG_3735.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>While the 43 cm width is standard for most bikes, the 46 cm and 50 cm widths would be great on an adventure, touring, or drop bar MTB.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"691\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_Specs_1024x1024.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_Specs_1024x1024.png?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_Specs_1024x1024.png?resize=768,518&amp;quality=75 768w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"481\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_All_web_1024x1024.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_All_web_1024x1024.png?w=1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/02/Walmer_Carbon_All_web_1024x1024.png?resize=768,361&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Sizes 43cm / 46cm / 50cm</li>\n<li>Weights 304g / 316g / 334g</li>\n<li>Torque Ratings Stem: Max. 6Nm</li>\n<li>Accessories: Max. 5Nm</li>\n<li>Controls: 6-8Nm</li>\n<li>Di2 Compatibility: Yes – Di2 Bar End Junction ready</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.curvecycling.com/products/carbon-walmer-bar?variant=42809612075184\" target=\"_blank\">Curve Cycling</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/curves-new-carbon-walmer-bar-is-wide-and-light/\">Curve Cycling’s New Carbon Walmer Bar is Wide and Light</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"b750c290db75f92a8598f960fa6d554e17bd0772817220e0f8f3a6b53bcce5aa","category":"Cycling"}